title: Cirque du Soleil - KA
description:
Recorded from German TV channel "ZDF theater" the show from Cirque du Soleil in the theater of the MGM Grand Hotel & Casino "KA".

The show in this recording is about 80 minutes long (I'm not shure if it's the whole show of KA) with a short introduction in German. So don't worry you don't have to learn German because only in the first 3 minutes is some German talking.


Codec: XVID
Resolution: 512 * 384
Audio: MP3 128kbit
